data.text:
SENIOR YEAR (2017-18)

Academic All-Big Ten ... placed 15th in the 400 IM at the Big Ten Championships with a NCAA B cut of 4:16.17 … also placed 15th in the 200 butterfly at Big Ten’s with a NCAA B cut of 1:58.66 … finished 38th in the 200 IM at the Big Ten Championships with a NCAA B cut of 2:01.69.

JUNIOR YEAR (2016-17)

Academic All-Big Ten … finished 11th in the 400 IM with a time of 4:13.65 at the Big Ten Championships ... placed 16th in the 200 butterfly at the Big Ten Championships with a time of 1:59.80 ... notched a 15th place finish in the 200 IM with a time of 2:00.03 at the Big Ten Championships ... touched first in the 200 butterfly (2:02.10) against Cincinnati ... won the 200 butterfly against Michigan State with a time of 2:02.32.

SOPHOMORE YEAR (2015-16)

Honorable-Mention CSCAA Scholar All-America ... Academic All-Big Ten … Finished eighth in the 400 IM at the Big Ten Championships with a time of 4:16.35 … placed 21st in the 200 butterfly at the Big Ten Championships with a time of 2:00.14 … 37th in the 200 IM at the Big Ten Championships with a mark of 2:02.32.

FRESHMAN YEAR (2014-15)

Scored points for the Hoosiers with a 15th place effort in the 200 fly at the Big Ten Championships with a 2:00.36 … placed 24th in the conference’s 200 IM after recording a career best, and NCAA B cut, time of 2:01.52 in the prelims … finished 14th in the Big Ten’s 400 IM with a time of 4:15.91, swam a career best and NCAA B cut time of 4:14.77 in the prelims … qualified for US Summer Nationals in the 200 butterfly.

PREP/PERSONAL

Top-eight state meet finalist in four events as a junior and senior at Homestead ... third in the 400 IM at the 2012 Minnesota Grand Prix ... team finished second at the state meet in 2012 ... holds school record in the 200 IM ... four-time all-conference selection ... earned All-America honors all four years ... earned academic Special Honors all four years ... is an artist, receiving honorable mention in Art and Writing Scholastics for 2014 ... parents are Ruth and Jim Cook ... born June 16, 1996.
